The table has columns for ID, Queue Start, Queue End, Subject, Status, Processed, Recipients, and Action, but there are no actual newsletter entries. There are also filter options available that would allow me to search for specific newsletters if there were any. Since I've successfully navigated to the Newsletter Queue page and can see the current state (empty queue), I should inform the user about what I found.
